OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774515911
OL,3,CBritish woman jailed in Iran gives
OL,4,Cfirst interview since the war began
OL,6,FLindsay Foreman told ITV News' Global
OL,7,FSecurity Editor Rohit Kachroo about
OL,8,Flife under bombardment in Iran's
OL,9,Fnotorious Evin prison
OL,11,FA British woman sentenced to ten years
OL,12,Fin jail by an Iranian court says she
OL,13,Fhas come to accept she may die behind
OL,14,Fbars, and fears the war could leave no
OL,15,Fone within the regime able to secure
OL,16,Fher release.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
