PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774515911
OL,3,CBritish woman jailed in Iran gives
OL,4,Cfirst interview since the war began
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FA routine has taken shape ` jogging
OL,12,Flaps of the prison courtyard as
OL,13,Ftraining for Parkruns, holding on to
OL,14,Fthe hope of release and the chance to
OL,15,Fcompete again in the UK. She says she
OL,16,Fremains "always optimistic."
OL,18,F"I've started running again, so this
OL,19,Fmorning I did fifty minutes of
OL,20,Frunning, which is about 7.5km."
OL,26,@xD@IOUxD@\O]zD@AOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774515911
OL,3,CBritish woman jailed in Iran gives
OL,4,Cfirst interview since the war began
OL,6,F"So even though I'm running around in
OL,7,Fa circle, each lap around the concrete
OL,8,Fcourtyard is 55 metres. So it's
OL,9,Frepetitive, but sometimes repetitive
OL,10,Fis good. You can switch off a little
OL,11,Fbit."
OL,13,FThe Foremans were sentenced last month
OL,14,Fafter more than a year in detention.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
